{"tid":1325570,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[區選］黃大仙上邨 之 決戰工聯會","createTime":"2019-07-17T02:21:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T05:22:24.000Z","uid":100228,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f976fc344ea976feeb397fb7b02226e881b23691","tid":1325570,"uid":100228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T02:21:14.000Z","msg":"代post<br />\n<br />\n眾所周知，龍上區一向係工聯會票倉，現屆區議員林文輝，當年胡志偉都輸比佢，而由於至今都未有非建制表示落場（白區），我地唔介意做炮灰，決定積極考慮參選 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">龍上區</span><br />\n<br />\n積極考慮參選原因：<br />\n1) 唔想見到有建制自動當選<br />\n2) 唔想因為自動當選而建制義工去其他區幫手<br />\n3) 想居民至少有得揀，同埋在過程中留低一些種子(可能係有啲人會繼續關心個區，唔一定係議員先爭取到改變)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而今次積極考慮參選有幾個原則：<br />\n1) 不屌票，打正分戰<br />\n2) 低成本，唔好chur 親自己友(包括人力時間金錢，如果其他區有更大機會，叫大家有心的去幫其他區)<br />\n3) 希望帶起一些議題或有心人，佢哋繼續自組或成為一些團體的成員繼續爭取都可以。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果有人都認同我以上的想法，都可以through以下條link，入住個group 先。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3ce04a03ba8fb5f6fee67256f526f49df099fa6","tid":1325570,"uid":35136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T02:28:38.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48eea53f59aaad2da1679f099ff91d73f0e3a866","tid":1325570,"uid":100228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T02:28:49.000Z","msg":"721 Admiralty"},{"pid":"ef22f9b3b4ccd2677636e9f2844d891ef1171f39","tid":1325570,"uid":81701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T02:30:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6443afd3be071505c899eab5291c57e3a624b67","tid":1325570,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T02:32:28.000Z","msg":"輸選票好過輸自動當選<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"332551